{"tid":2007781,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警甴：好撚嬲 事件對其他一直盡忠職守的同事非常不公","createTime":"2020-05-08T14:01:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T14:24:38.000Z","uid":216992,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7dd35647d0a322106f545c74a930423794cffd2f","tid":2007781,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T14:01:17.000Z","msg":"【 警方嚴肅跟進警務人員違法違紀行為 】<br />\n<br />\n     就近日有警務人員涉嫌干犯違法違紀行為，警隊管理層高度關注並立案調查，先後拘捕多名涉及案件的警務人員，當中涉嫌干犯嚴重罪行的被捕人已被或將被停職。<br />\n <br />\n     對於有警務人員涉嫌違法違紀，警方感到十分憤怒。事件影響市民對警隊的信心，對其他一直盡忠職守的同事非常不公，警方對此感到失望和痛心。<br />\n<br />\n     警方高度重視人員的紀律和操守，警務人員不論職級高低，均須遵守法紀。對於任何違法違紀行為，警隊管理層堅決採取零容忍的態度，並要求監管人員嚴格履行督導責任。就所有違法違紀的個案，警方承諾會嚴肅調查和秉公處理，絕不偏私。<br />\n <br />\n     警隊一直重視警務人員的誠信管理，投訴及內部調查科於多年前制訂了「誠信管理綜合綱領」，致力推廣人員正直及誠實的品格，監管人員的紀律和操守。為避免同類事件發生，警隊管理層正重新審視警隊的內部管理策略。<br />\n <br />\n     警方重申，絕不容許警隊有害群之馬，如有任何人員涉嫌違法違紀，警方會按照既定機制嚴肅跟進，作出調查和採取適當行動。"},{"pid":"09d7018136a0510f2fcf5304ecac067e16b98ea8","tid":2007781,"uid":63934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T14:01:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6e82f9c9d267ff59ac600d209443ff2669886fd","tid":2007781,"uid":216992,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T14:02:19.000Z","msg":"事件影響市民對警隊的信心<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n未訓醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />半年前開始已經無<br />\n<br />\n721 都已經無<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b729a3e19b6fc295d2618b1f7e895d7e25ab12d2","tid":2007781,"uid":103325,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T14:02:47.000Z","msg":"好撚嬲&hellip;乜佢地咁死蠢會俾人捉到架，醒 d 咪無事囉"},{"pid":"2a5101304b8bd2baeacea270bb1498fbf1faf225","tid":2007781,"uid":216992,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T14:03:05.000Z","msg":"警務人員不論職級高低，均須遵守法紀。對於任何違法違紀行為，警隊管理層堅決採取零容忍的態度<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁陶輝呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bca502cb2a8180fdfa04758efe55172f1a88b07","tid":2007781,"uid":216992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T14:04:00.000Z","msg":"絕不容許警隊有害群之馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"888576409ee9cff425df8b94c5ef8ca584705932","tid":2007781,"uid":62514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b729a3e19b6fc295d2618b1f7e895d7e25ab12d2","tid":2007781,"uid":103325,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T14:02:47.000Z","msg":"好撚嬲&hellip;乜佢地咁死蠢會俾人捉到架，醒 d 咪無事囉"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T14:04:10.000Z","msg":"擺明傾唔成分贜 所以比人督岀黎啦"},{"pid":"e419723315dbd648e4f580aa19709922541a9c6c","tid":2007781,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T14:04:40.000Z","msg":"「誠信管理綜合綱領」<br />\n<br />\n第一次聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb086b6fa1d5ec7204732d35cee5302e14bd085f","tid":2007781,"uid":185656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T14:04:56.000Z","msg":"支持警察以死明志<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":